description:
-Changed the guitar for AN ACTUAL GUITAR, NOT AN ORGAN (WHY?)
-Remade the bass from a tab I found on guitarpro, and added the slides at the beginning
-Remade the drums by ear (I think they're 90% accurate)
-Added some bends to the vocals, now they resemble the song a little more
Slowed down the tempo 86bpm to 77bpm (according to the web, that's the actual tempo)
-The only issue is that now that I added a triplet feel, the guitar isn't accurate on certain bars, but apart from that everything else sounds better.
title: Cry Baby Cry
